  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>Welcome to <strong>Wanderlust</strong>, your go-to travel listing app. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app or visit our website.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Info:</strong> When you create an account, we collect your name, email, and optional profile photo.</li>
    <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> If enabled, we use your location to show nearby destinations and listings.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We log interactions such as searches, clicks, and bookings to improve the app experience.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Info:</strong> This includes IP address, browser type, and device model for analytics and security.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To display travel listings relevant to your interests and location.</li>
    <li>To personalize recommendations and content.</li>
    <li>To manage your bookings and notify you of trip updates.</li>
    <li>To improve app performance and fix bugs.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing of Data</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal data. We only share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Hosts and partners when you interact or book with them.</li>
    <li>Trusted third-party services (like analytics or hosting providers).</li>
    <li>Law enforcement or regulatory bodies when required by law.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Your Privacy Choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You can update or delete your profile anytime.</li>
    <li>You can turn off location sharing in your device settings.</li>
    <li>You can unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We use secure servers and encryption to protect your data, but please note that no internet transmission is ever 100% secure.</p>

  <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>Wanderlust is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We’ll post any changes on this page with a new effective date.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have questions or concerns, email us at: <a href="mailto:support@wanderlustapp.com">support@wanderlustapp.com</a></p>

